By BO Staff Writer Andile Mngxitama does a moving presentation on land tenure. He is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization which he has also aptly described as “the reincarnation of Bambatha and the Mau Mau all rolled into one”. The full presentation may be viewed on YouTube via the link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UOgYs3dA5rI No related posts.